ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 273, Nova Scotia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 273 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to NOVA SCOTIA with respect to the winter storm that occurred from February 2 to February 5, 2024.
